source.name: City College of San Francisco Budget Forecast (2010-11 and 2011-12)
source.description: This is a draft spreadsheet presented to the Board of Trustees Budget Committee meeting on May 19, 2010 by the Office of Vice Chancellor of Finance and Administration forecasting the District's budget for the 2010-11 and 2011-12 fiscal years and identifying anticipated deltas in expenditures for 2010-11. The College is expected to pass an preliminary budget at its June board meeting.
